text: Jordan de Vogelaere (born 8 September 1996) is a Belgian korfball player. He is a member of Boeckenberg KC and the Belgium national korfball team. De Vogelaere played for the club in the Dutch national Korfbal League. He returned to Belgium in 2021 playing with Boeckenberg KC. With the national team he won the silver medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===National team=== ; World Games : 2017 World Games : 2022 World Games ; IKF World Korfball Championship : 2019 IKF World Korfball Championship ; European Korfball Championship : 4th 2018 IKF European Korfball A-Championship : 2021 IKF European Korfball A-Championship ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian korfball players
